docs/index.rst
     1‚Üí``pluggy``
     2‚Üí==========
     3‚Üí**The pytest plugin system**
     4‚Üí
     5‚ÜíWhat is it?
     6‚Üí***********
     7‚Üí``pluggy`` is the crystallized core of :ref:`plugin management and hook
     8‚Üícalling <pytest:writing-plugins>` for :std:doc:`pytest <pytest:index>`.
     9‚ÜíIt enables `1400+ plugins`_ to extend and customize ``pytest``'s default
    10‚Üíbehaviour. Even ``pytest`` itself is composed as a set of ``pluggy`` plugins
    11‚Üíwhich are invoked in sequence according to a well defined set of protocols.
    12‚Üí
    13‚ÜíIt gives users the ability to extend or modify the behaviour of a
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶

